\q
\v 5 Trust in Jehovah with all thy heart, 
\q And lean not upon thine own understanding: 
\q
\v 6 In all thy ways acknowledge him, 
\q And he will direct thy paths. 
\q
\v 7 Be not wise in thine own eyes; 
\q Fear Jehovah, and depart from evil: 
\q
\v 8 It will be health to thy navel, 
