\b
\q
\v 20 My son, attend to my words; 
\q Incline thine ear unto my sayings. 
\q
\v 21 Let them not depart from thine eyes; 
\q Keep them in the midst of thy heart. 
\q
\v 22 For they are life unto those that find them, 
